v0.56.0: gentle feature tips

- a subtle assistant: a small pill fades in at the top now and then with one fun thing to try (stargaze, photo mode, follow a critter, speed up time, weather, species race, drinking, AI narration...)
- non-invasive: doesn't block clicks, auto-fades after ~9s, long gaps between tips, and hides entirely in photo mode
- new src/ui/tips.ts, cycles randomly without repeating
